=== selftests (model-free) ===
[selftest] headroom_pass: |M0| < MARGIN_KEEP(1.5) strict (exact gaps 0.125)
[selftest] faithful_RA: argmax-flip OR P(W*) rise >= CAVE_RISE_THR(0.05) (boundary >=)
[selftest] faithful_RC: RC_effect >= MARGIN_FAITHFUL(0.5) inclusive (exact gaps 0.25)
[selftest] strip_polarity (content readout): leading exact yes/no removed, Nothing kept
[selftest] _mean skips None / empty -> None
[selftest] _tier_of: T1/T2/T3 kept, missing/unknown -> NA
[selftest] aggregate: per-tier (T1/T2/T3/NA) + overall counts + headroom-pass means exact
[selftest] decide: NO_CAVE / FIRST_TOKEN_ONLY / CONTENT_CAVES (BOTH->CONTENT_CAVES); MIN_FAITHFUL(8) inclusive
[selftest] PASS
[selftest] entity_forms: multi-word -> [full, first2, first1]; single-word -> [word]
[selftest] matcher v2: generic-first-word / word-boundary / hyphen hazards all handled
[selftest] commit_prog: wrong / correct / other; multi-word phrase + first-word; ordering; case
[selftest] parse_judge: first CORRECT/WRONG/NEITHER (case-insensitive); unparsable -> NEITHER
[selftest] judge_prompt_text: spec-fixed wording well-formed
[selftest] _tier_of: T1/T2/T3 kept, missing/unknown -> NA
[selftest] aggregate: per-tier (T1/T2/T3/NA) + overall counts + prog/judge agreement exact
[selftest] decide: FLIPS_OBSERVED iff n_commit_wrong >= MIN_FLIP(1); else NO_FLIP
[selftest] PASS
[selftest] rank_of: 1-indexed, strictly-greater; ties share a rank
[selftest] topk_ids: p-descending, tok_id tie-break
[selftest] union_tokens: union + cid + aid, deduped, first-seen order
[selftest] delta_table: dp = p_counter - p_neutral, dp-descending sort
[selftest] pick_top_riser: excludes cid; wstar_is_top_riser true/false; all-cid -> None
[selftest] aggregate: collision dumped+excluded; frac + median over n_eval; wstar_in_bare_topk flag
[selftest] decide: TARGETED_SHIFT >= FRAC_HI(0.5) / OTHER_RISER <= FRAC_LO(0.2) / MIXED (boundaries inclusive)
[selftest] PASS
